ongoli played a prominent role as the attorney generals legal advisor including participation in formulating the patriot act and drafting the administrations order authorizing military commissions to try suspected terrorists and writing the subsequent regulations in  the white house chief of staff andy card named ciongoli as the administrations chief liaison to the independent  commission some democratic members of the commission criticized ciongoli for restricting the commissions access to key people and documents after leaving the justice department later that year mr ciongoli became a senior vice president and general counsel at time warner europe when his former boss judge alito was nominated to the united states supreme court ciongoli played an active role in preparing alito for his confirmation hearings and in publicly advocating the nominationcitation needed in a surprising move ciongoli then left his lucrative corporate job to become one of the newly confirmed justice alitos law clerks justice alito officiated mr ciongolis marriage in june  mr ciongoli went on to be general counsel of a number of wellknown public companies postclerkship including willis group holdings plc  lincoln financial group  and since july  general counsel of the campbell soup company referencesedit  counseling ashcroft  legal times   where’s saddam  msnbc newsweek in iraq  archived september   at the wayback machine  new gc at aoltime warner europe reports to his former professor  corporate counsel magazine  alitos murder board a mix of the legal elite  national law journal   lane charles  alito hires as a clerk former ashcroft aide washington post   lattman peter  justice alito marries off his law clerk wall street journal  retrieved from httpsenwikipediaorgwindexphptitleadamgciongolioldid categories  birthsliving peopleunited states department of justice lawyersunited states senate lawyerspeople from burlington vermontamerican people of italian descentuniversity of pennsylvania alum