perspective and look forward to working with him to build on the strong foundation we have established with our legal department” ciongoli  joins campbell with more than  years of legal experience most recently he was executive vice president and general counsel of lincoln financial group a fortune  insurance and financial services company where he directed the law compliance corporate secretary and government relations departments prior to lincoln financial he served as group general counsel and secretary for willis group holdings plc during his tenure at willis group he supported the company’s global operations and advised the company on several significant transactions adam was also senior vice president and general counsel for time warner europe he was responsible for negotiating regulatory clearance of european mergers and acquisitions his previous experience includes serving as the counselor to the attorney general of the united states as chief counsel to the us senate subcommittee on the constitution federalism and property rights and as law clerk to united states supreme court justice samuel a alito jr “i am very excited to partner with denise morrison and join the campbell team” said ciongoli “it is an honor to be able to contribute in a leadership role in the future development of such an iconic and important american company” ciongoli graduated from the university of pennsylvania with a bachelor of arts in history he holds a juris doctor magna cum laude from the georgetown university law center ciongoli is a member of the board of directors for the habitat for humanity in philadelphia he also serves as a lecturerinlaw at columbia university law school about campbell soup company campbell nysecpb is driven and inspired by our purpose “real food that matters for life’s moments” the company makes a range of products from highquality soups and simple meals to snacks and healthy beverages for generations people have trusted campbell to provide authentic flavorful and readily available foods and beverages that connect them to each other to warm memories and to what’s important today led by its iconic campbell’s brand the company’s portfolio includes pepperidge farm goldfish bolthouse farms v swanson prego pace plum organics arnott’s tim tam royal dansk and kjeldsens founded in  campbell has a heritage of giving back and acting as a good steward of the planet’s natural resources the company is a member of the standard  poor’s  and the dow jones sustainability indexes for more information visit wwwcampbellsoupcompanycom or follow company news on twitter via campbellsoupco view source version on businesswirecom httpwwwbusinesswirecomnewshomeen source campbell soup company campbell soup companyinvestor contactjennifer driscoll jenniferdriscollcampbellsoupcomormedia contactcarla burigatto carlaburigattocampbellsoupcom press release archive july june may april march february january  december november october september august july june may april march february january  november october september august july june may april march february january  november october september august july june may april march february january  december november october september august july june may april march february january  december november october september august july june may april march february january  november october september august july june may april march february january  november october september august july june may april march february january  december november october september august july june may april march february january  december november october september august july june may april march february january  december november october september august july june may april march february january  november september august july june may april march february  november september august july june may april march february january  december november september august july june may march february january  december november october